{"type": "article", "id": 27849, "title": "蒲草椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-07T06:51:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164604tWhDbn4c1SKfaCe8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>一到夏天，不少人会搬出凉席椅来乘凉，对远在英国的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.christopher-jenner.com/\">Christopher Jenner</a> 来说，一张蒲草椅更是结合了古老的编织工艺和现代技术，有着非同寻常的意义。这张名为 Rush（即蒲草的英文）的座椅由 Jenner 和欧洲仅存的几位蒲草织工之一 <a href=\"http://www.rushmatters.co.uk/\">Felicity Irons</a> 合作打造，从收割蒲草到制作完成共花费了 12 个月的时间。座椅的框架由 28 片经过五轴 CNC 加工的英国橡木组件构成，中间嵌入了织工手工编织的座椅，充满了匠心。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164602IM9H7VEn3jXeQDpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164602u1AjUWzBZLdNDonF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164603PyYiSzUrk2WfQGI1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164604bcyqB59UgVHPdfaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}